data.value: Bill Bourbon's Niece. Deborah U. Taunt was close family to Bill Bourbon, but never spent much time around his side of the family. Deb claims that Mr. Bourbon's wife Beatrix never liked her, and told him not to include her side of the family in the will, which according to Deb would leave all of his money for Beatrix and their kids. Deb wishes she had been closer to her Uncle, and misses the days before Beatrix was around.
